msgstr "この変数はウィンドウ分割により新たに親ウィンドウを作成させるかどうかを制御する。以下の値が認識される:"

#. type: table
#: original_texis/windows.texi:1535
msgid "This means that the new live window is allowed to share the existing parent window, if one exists, provided the split occurs in the same direction as the existing window combination (otherwise, a new internal window is created anyway)."
