#: original_texis/windows.texi:1542
msgid "This means that @code{display-buffer} makes a new parent window when it splits a window and is passed a @code{window-height} or @code{window-width} entry in the @var{alist} argument (@pxref{Buffer Display Action Functions}).  Otherwise, window splitting behaves as for a value of @code{nil}."
